{"tid":1481831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚就割撚晒身邊啲港豬","createTime":"2019-08-18T00:56:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T14:49:10.000Z","uid":131766,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"13ea7b706921948b3c5e604373ff65436458a65f","tid":1481831,"uid":131766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T00:56:28.000Z","msg":"身邊好多垃圾兩個幾月一次都冇出過黎<br />\n或者係樓上嘆緊冷氣 影落街打句加油<br />\n打堆鳩嘢好撚煽情咁 自己就周圍去玩<br />\n呢刻仲話示威者打人就係錯 昏迷咗幾耐啊<br />\n以為自己站係道德高地其實係你離撚晒地<br />\n咁撚大愛點解唔出黎啊點解唔用愛去擋子彈<br />\n<br />\n你地真係好撚嘔心 睇清楚晒你地<br />\n今晚開ig 睇到邊個今日走咗去玩<br />\n我就將你班仆街冇人性政治冷感港豬中立閪<br />\n歸類為黑狗嘅朋友 <br />\n我嘅餘生同你班垃圾勢不兩立<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NubAJsg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNubAJsg.jpg&h=31702c5d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ArHPNTW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FArHPNTW.jpg&h=ed5faa0c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9297d832965a172af3b29570359a0648dec0c70","tid":1481831,"uid":274336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T01:06:16.000Z","msg":"有冇努力同化佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都係7月中先同化咗我另一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"728c406af4bd4a136a10cbf5e030b4ff012b2af3","tid":1481831,"uid":131766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d9297d832965a172af3b29570359a0648dec0c70","tid":1481831,"uid":274336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T01:06:16.000Z","msg":"有冇努力同化佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都係7月中先同化咗我另一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTim